2026-04-27T19:03:10.9190044Z 30    <!--
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9190679Z 31        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9191650Z 32        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9192849Z 33        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9193828Z 34        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9195118Z 35        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
