2026-04-27T19:03:10.9199332Z 38-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9200210Z 39    <!--
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9200813Z 40        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9201568Z 41        across Android versions:
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9202257Z 42          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9203090Z 43            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9203929Z 44            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9204999Z 45          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9205862Z 46            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9206741Z 47        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9207601Z 48        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9208396Z 49        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9209017Z 50    -->
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9209659Z 51    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-04-27T19:03:10.9210726Z 51-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
