2026-04-27T19:03:11.2860404Z 40        across Android versions:
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2860740Z 41          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2861038Z 42            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2861369Z 43            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2861683Z 44          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2862178Z 45            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2862511Z 46        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2862836Z 47        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2863114Z 48        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-27T19:03:11.2863273Z 49    -->
